  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium-high heat",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together sesame oil, soy sauce, rice vinegar, grated ginger, and garlic",
    "Add the wagyu beef to the bowl and marinate for at least 30 minutes",
    "Thread the marinated beef onto skewers, leaving a small space between each piece",
    "Grill the skewers for 3-4 minutes per side, or until they reach an internal temperature of 130 degrees",
    "Let the skewers rest for 5 minutes before serving",
    "Garnish with green onions and sesame seeds"
  ],
